[0.000, "o", "# what they do.  They're here only as hints or reminders.  If you are unsure\r\u001b[12d# consult the online docs. You have been warned.\r\u001b[13d#\u001b[14d\b# Configuration and logfile names: If the filenames you specify for many\r\u001b[15d# of the server's control files begin with \"/\" (or \"drive:/\" for Win32), the\r\u001b[16d"]
